## How to Extract Details (Length & Verbatim Rules) ##

-> For each distinct agency or guideline, identify the most critical sentences that capture the core compliance statement, submission requirement, or ethical standard.
-> Extract ONLY those critical sentences verbatim from the text. And keep the details field short 2 sentences max.
-> Keep details short.
-> Combine them into a single string for the "details" field.
-> Do NOT rewrite or summarize in your own words.
-> Do NOT include unrelated sentences that do not pertain to that specific agency/guideline.

Important:
agency_name = specific regulatory body, guideline, or lowest-level section name  
details = key regulatory verbatim statements merged into one string  

Both must be exact verbatim from the extracted text.

